{"tid":600561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵月內兩炒扶手梯　靚女乘客：「梗係擔心」 03月21日(三) 18:14","createTime":"2018-03-21T11:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T11:59:04.000Z","uid":162303,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cee35c29674575fd4b8423afdc028ce317c68d","tid":600561,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:51:08.000Z","msg":"港鐵一個月內兩度發生炒扶手梯意外，不少乘客均對此非常擔心，其中乘客譚小姐指，留意到近年發生多宗扶手電梯意外，當中更有個案令乘客受傷，擔心同類事件接踵而來。她又表示，由於內地曾發生乘客墮踏板喪命事件，故她經過時都會盡快檻過，並會留意梯邊有否卡住異物。她又指，港鐵近年不斷加價，但故障有增無減，強烈要求港鐵改善服務，確保乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n對於是次扶手電梯意外險令市民受傷，乘客汪小姐坦言「梗係擔心啦」，故於乘搭時亦會望住扶手電梯，安全至上。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/21/195045_690e9050cdc6b4b7be930e5b9aaf920a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2F195045_690e9050cdc6b4b7be930e5b9aaf920a.jpg&h=260ad645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180321/bkn-20180321181434185-0321_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180321%2Fbkn-20180321181434185-0321_00822_001.html&d=0rB%2F2xn9mIVBeqRBA0yYbb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=6d290038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180321/bkn-20180321181434185-0321_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b6c7727bd5ed100d7c32f1c03c5f40f88e07cf82","tid":600561,"uid":110110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"一起底可能又係做雞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0492266c5e2a8585b9760c1a510bd0d4defade36","tid":600561,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor